informaltable.tgroup:
&dircols;
&keyhead;




Note that element and level can be specified more than once in this directive.


Note that if a single element name is matched with a list of level names, or vice versa, the single name must be given first. Multiple element and level name lists should have the same number.



Note that category_attribute and category can be specified more than once in this directive, and that category_cascade determines how to combine more than one instance.

&dircols;
&pkeyhead;



Note that line_width, line_style, outline and fill can be specified more than once in this directive, for drawing multi-coloured curves!
